Notes on Julia and Pluto Mechanics for ComputationalThinking Course
=================================================================

Notes on Running Pluto Notebook
------------------------------

- start a terminal, 
    - and ideally change directory to the project area, so the Pluto notebook can easily find the files
- start a Julia REPL (Julia 1.4+)
    - `$ julia`
- load the Pluto library and execute Pluto

    ```{julia}
    > import Pluto
    > Pluto.run()
    ```